{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSToolBarTopV","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSToolBarTop"}],"platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","beta":false,"name":"iOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"name":"visionOS"}],"title":"OUDSToolBarTop","symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSToolBarTop","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The top toolbar (aka "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"navigation bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" on iOS and iPadOS 18 and lower) sits at the top of the screen and provides contextual information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and controls related to the current view."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It typically displays the page title, and may include navigation actions such as “Back” or “Close” as well as supplementary actions."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It can contains leading and trailing actions."}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop\/init(title:hasLargeTitle:subtitle:leadingItems:trailingItems:)"]},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop\/body(content:)"],"title":"Instance Methods"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop\/ViewModifier-Implementations"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI12ViewModifierP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSToolBarTop","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"toolBarTop(_:hasLargeTitle:subtitle:leadingItems:trailingItems:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"  View helper applies a SwiftUI toolbar configuration.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Appearances","anchor":"Appearances","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With Liquid Glass \/ iOS 26+ the OS will change the rendering of the toolbar items depending to the context:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The OS can group the items of same types in one group with kind of rectangle (e.g. views with menus)","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"But for buttons items they will remain isolated","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The placement of the title can be leading or centered depending to the length of the text","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The text can be truncated if there is not enough remaining space","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The OS can apply another style for the back button","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Without Liquid Glass \/ iOS 18 and lower, the OS won’t change that much the style of the toolbar items, Items won’t be visually grouped."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Globaly the appearence of the * navigation bar* elements is changed by the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsNavigationBarAppearance"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"helper of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" that must be applyed on the root view of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NavigationStack"},{"type":"text","text":" for example."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Technical constraints","anchor":"Technical-constraints","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To be sure for iOS 18 and lower the back buttton and text have the good color, in your main view apply the following accent color:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    struct AppMainView: View {","        var body: some View {","            ContentView()","                .accentColor(theme.colors.contentDefault)","        }","    }"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Platform considerations","anchor":"Platform-considerations","level":2},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component is available on iOS, iPadOS, and visionOS","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component is not available for watchOS, tvOS and macOS","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Badges uses","anchor":"Badges-uses","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For iOS 26 with Liquid Glass, the system badge is used because the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge"},{"type":"text","text":" does not provide a suitable rendering with the glassified effect applied on the top toolbar."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS until 18 and without Liquid Glass "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge"},{"type":"text","text":" is always used."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Code sample","anchor":"Code-sample","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    ContentView()","        .toolBarTop(\"Title\",","            leadingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(navigation: .back())","            },","            trailingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(label: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","                OUDSToolBarItem(icon: Image(decorative: \"some_image\"), accessibilityLabel: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","            }","        )"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-ios-tool-bar-top"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2},{"type":"heading","text":"Liquid Glass","anchor":"Liquid-Glass","level":3},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_Orange_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_Orange_dark"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange Compact","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_dark"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_